strings: <se_low>Yangus: This is the first time I've 'ad to climb a mountain as tough as this!

<se_high>Jessica: We must be getting close to the summit now.
And when we get there, we're going to have to fight Gemon!<page>Jessica: Let's hurry up and get this over with!
<se_def>Angelo: If I'd known it was this hard to get to, I'd never have made such a rash promise to go and save this stupid egg.

<se_def>Angelo: ...Er, I was just having a little grumble to myself.
I don't really mean it.
<se_high>Red: Wot, you out o' puff already? That's a bit naff. Come on, pull yer socks up!

<se_low>Morrie: Ah ha ha! You young ones get tired easy, ay?
Not Moro Mozzarella! I can keep going all nighties!
